 >
 
 
 
 
 
 
 <span class="author">Comment
 
 by 
 
 <a style="white-space: nowrap" href="/u//">mcintosh...@gmail.com</a>,
 
 </span>
 <span class="date" title="Mon Mar  3 16:31:13 2008">Mar 3, 2008</span>
 <div>
<div class="commentcontent">
<p>Could you add a sentence or two explaining what these are about? Some are very clear; others aren&#x27;t. </p>
</div>
 
 
 </div>
 </div>
 

 
 <div class="artifactcomment"
 
 >
 
 
 
 
 
 
 <span class="author">Comment
 
 by 
 
 <a style="white-space: nowrap" href="/u/111419116640903839175/">mr.m.kau...@gmail.com</a>,
 
 </span>
 <span class="date" title="Tue Mar  4 17:39:16 2008">Mar 4, 2008</span>
 <div>
<div class="commentcontent">
<p>How do I UNINSTALL this?  You say how to install, but how do I entirely remove it from my system at some later date?  I like to know that about something before I just go ahead and install it. </p>
</div>
 
 
 </div>
 </div>
 

 
 <div class="artifactcomment"
 
 >
 
 
 
 
 
 
 <span class="author">Comment
 
 by 
 
 <a style="white-space: nowrap" href="/u/117967714857604033296/">jacob...@gmail.com</a>,
 
 </span>
 <span class="date" title="Wed Mar  5 03:26:07 2008">Mar 5, 2008</span>
 <div>
<div class="commentcontent">
<p>To uninstall Secrets.prefPane, simply right click (control-click) on the icon in the view all part of system preferences. Then click remove in the list (should be the only thing in the list).  </p>
</div>
 
 
 </div>
 </div>
 

 
