 <div class="artifactcomment"
 
 >
 
 
 
 
 
 
 <span class="author">Comment
 
 by 
 
 <a style="white-space: nowrap" href="/u/107969392794240628950/">chris.ta...@gmail.com</a>,
 
 </span>
 <span class="date" title="Sun Jul  6 11:28:46 2008">Jul 6, 2008</span>
 <div>
<div class="commentcontent">
<p>If you turned up your sound, you would hear someone saying whatever&#x27;s in the focused area. You&#x27;ve turned on VoiceOver<a href="/p/blacktree-secrets/w/edit/VoiceOver">?</a> by mistake. Go to System Preferences, Universal Access, and turn off VoiceOver<a href="/p/blacktree-secrets/w/edit/VoiceOver">?</a>. </p>
</div>
 
 
 </div>
 </div>
 

 
